OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCatholic Church honours    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FPolish family who hid Jews 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A beatification Mass service has been  
OL,6, held in Poland for a Catholic family   
OL,7, murdered by Nazis for hiding Jews      
OL,8, during World War Two.                  
OL,10,FPoland's president and more than 30,000
OL,11,Fpilgrims attended the outdoor service, 
OL,12,Fled by Pope Francis' envoy.            
OL,14,FThis was the first time an entire      
OL,15,Ffamily has been beatified, a great     
OL,16,Fhonour and a step towards sainthood.   
OL,18,FThey were executed in 1944 with the    
OL,19,FJews they sheltered in south-eastern   
OL,20,FPoland, after they were betrayed.      
